{"type": "article", "id": 19220, "title": "带蓝牙音响的橱柜", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-17T07:40:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145835CNS5HElKUTQi6L8R.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个带蓝牙音响的橱柜，39 英寸宽的扬声器占据了一个柜门，喇叭的形状类似于一个留声机，有特别的时尚感。扬声器是陶瓷做的，有红、黄、粉、绿、白等多个亮丽的颜色，另有一款用 18 世纪橡木搭配 24k 镀金扬声器，追求复古的感觉。意大利设计师 Paolo Cappello 想要让音乐回归到原始的状态，同时拥有强烈的辨识度。<a href=\"http://www.miniforms.com/en/products/4_buffet-and-cabinet/177_caruso/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145819j91k5byCYGsTdZ6c.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.85574572\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145820FI6dNjKTu1CPH7aY.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1091\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145820HQGBg789RKTsnXyP.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"999\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.22127139\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145822AGTn7zRPL1rBYvi6.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1091\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}